jury, The Charlotte Observer reported, quoting sources familiar
with the PTL investigation.
   The government's latest targets apparently are witnesses who may
have perjured themselves before a special grand jury that indicted
Bakker, Dortch and two other PTL associates.
   The names of the witnesses were not disclosed. Bakker himself
