seeking an outside investor to provide it with a capital infusion
and reduce American Express Co.'s 61 percent stake in Shearson.
   The restructuring announced Wednesday, which had been expected,
comes as Shearson confronts the fallout from a major expansion
strategy that has been shaken by a downturn in the securities
industry.
