requesting federal approval to acquire at least 25 percent of USX
Corp.
   In a filing Wednesday with the Securities and Exchange
Commission, Icahn revealed that he was seeking permission from the
Federal Trade Commission to increase his stake in the
Pittsburgh-based oil, gas and steel company.
   According to the SEC filing, Icahn owns nearly 34 million of
